V0117_01_00_00_0.text: Whenever things get rough, I start to doubt myself.

V0117_01_00_00_1.text:
But no more!
Time to toughen up!

V0117_01_00_01_0.text: I'm sick of always being scared!

V0117_01_00_01_1.text:
I'm gonna face my fear!
And win!

V0117_01_00_03_0.text: Jay! You're my best bud, but I won't let you steamroll me!

V0117_03_00_01_0.text:
Oh yeah!
Even I can't mess this up!

V0117_03_00_04_0.text:
I don't like my odds...
But I refuse to lose!

V0117_03_00_05_0.text: If I can just survive this...

V0117_05_00_00_0.text: Jay draws the card he needs 'cause he believes in his deck!

V0117_05_00_00_1.text:
So I'll believe in mine too!
I draw!

V0117_08_00_00_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Weapon Change!

V0117_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Shield Crush!

V0117_08_00_02_1.text: I destroy one monster in Defense Position!

V0117_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Spell, Vehicroid Connection Zone!

V0117_08_00_04_1.text: My Special Summoned monster can't be destroyed by effects!

V0117_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Machine Conversion Factory!

V0117_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Spell!
Pot of Greed!

V0117_08_00_08_0.text:
This card will get me out of a jam!
Monster Reborn!

V0117_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Emergency Provisions!

V0117_08_00_10_1.text: I gain 1000 LP for each Spell and Trap I send to the grave!

V0117_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Welcome to Megaroid City!

V0117_08_00_13_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, Limiter Removal!

V0117_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Polymerization!

V0117_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate a Quick-Play Spell!
Mystical Space Typhoon!

V0117_08_00_17_0.text:
I'll play my Spell Card.
I activate Stop Defense!

V0117_08_00_24_0.text:
Too bad!
It's my Trap Card, Trap Hole!

V0117_08_00_25_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Magic Cylinder!

V0117_08_00_25_1.text: I'll send the attack right back at you!

V0117_08_00_26_1.text: All monsters in Attack Position switch to Defense Position!

V0117_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Emergeroid Call!

V0117_08_00_28_0.text: I activate Call of the Haunted to resurrect my monster!

V0117_08_00_29_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Micro Ray!

V0117_09_00_00_1.text: All Spell and Trap Cards on the field are banished!

V0117_09_00_01_1.text: I add two "roid" monsters in my Graveyard to my hand!

V0117_09_00_02_1.text: I Special Summon the "roid" that was added to my hand!

V0117_09_00_03_0.text: Barbaroid, the Ultimate Battle Machine's effect activates!

V0117_09_00_05_0.text: Super Vehicroid - Stealth Union's effect activates!

V0117_09_00_06_0.text: Super Vehicroid - Mobile Base's effect activates!

V0117_09_00_07_1.text: After it battles, it destroys one Spell or Trap Card!

V0117_09_00_08_1.text: Truckroid equips the monster it destroyed!

V0117_09_00_09_1.text: Your Defense Position monster is destroyed!

V0117_09_00_14_1.text: I Special Summon the destroyed monster in Defense Position!

V0117_09_00_15_1.text: When a "roid" is wrecked in battle, it returns to the hand!

V0117_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0117_13_00_02_0.text: Ambulanceroid is coming to the rescue!

V0117_13_00_03_0.text: Combine into Barbaroid, the Ultimate Battle Machine!

V0117_13_00_08_0.text: Super Vehicroid Jumbo Drill is digging this way!

V0117_13_00_09_0.text: Unite into one, Super Vehicroid - Stealth Union!

V0117_13_00_10_0.text: Transform into Super Vehicroid - Mobile Base!

V0117_13_00_11_0.text:
This is my favorite card!
Steam Gyroid!

V0117_13_00_30_0.text:
*blush* This is my card crush!
Thunder Nyan Nyan!

V0117_13_00_31_0.text:
She's not Ms. Dorothy playing dress up!
She's the real deal!

V0117_13_00_31_1.text: Your hero and mine: Dark Magician Girl!

V0117_19_00_31_0.text: I still can't believe I'm using the REAL Dark Magician Girl!

V0117_21_00_02_0.text: Just because I'm ending my turn doesn't mean I'm giving up!

V0117_28_00_00_0.text: I feel like my skills are getting better with every Duel.

V0117_28_00_01_0.text: A Duel isn't over 'til the last card is played!

V0117_28_00_01_1.text:
Jay taught me that!
And he's right!

V0117_28_00_03_0.text: Jaden, thanks for teaching me to never give up.

V0117_28_00_03_1.text: I don't know who I'd be without you!

V0117_29_00_00_0.text: Everyone's Dueling skills have improved... except for me...

V0117_29_00_01_0.text:
Sigh...
I guess it's bye-bye Sy...

V0117_29_00_02_0.text:
Sigh...
But I won't run and hide like I used to!

V0117_29_00_03_1.text:
But I'll defeat you someday!
And sooner than you think!

V0117_30_00_00_0.text: I might look small, but I Duel big!

V0117_30_00_01_0.text: You're more pathetic than I am!

V0117_30_00_02_0.text: I’ll cram your tough talk in a box and mail it back to you!

V0117_33_00_01_0.text: I won't let you beat me!

V0117_34_00_04_0.text:
That's my card crush!
It never lets me down in a pinch!

V0117_34_00_06_0.text:
I'm gonna fight my fear!
...Just not now.

V0117_34_00_08_0.text:
Please tell me you're done.
Pretty please?

V0117_35_00_00_0.text: I'll give it all I got!

V0117_35_00_01_0.text: You can count on me and my Vehicroids!
